= Code

This project was developed under continuous version control using Git and is
hosted on GitHub at
#link("https://github.com/arnauKL/pd_datscan_cnn_thesis")[arnauKL/pd_datscan_cnn_thesis].
The repository contains the preprocessing pipeline, model implementations,
training scripts, evaluation utilities, and experiment configuration files used
throughout the thesis.

